Erasing Zend_Filter_Dir/Basename/Realpath in favor of Zend_Filter_Callback ?</p>

<p>You may have noted that Zend_Filter_Realpath provides options and additionally it does not only call realpath but it also other OS specific operations.</p>

<p>Also to note that for usability it's better to have $addFilter('Basename'); than $addFilter('Callback', false, array('basename')); even if this means to add 10 lines of code. ;-)</p>

